oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Amatuer Boxing Assoc. Job No. 37847
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2391) for an order placed for the Nashville Amateur Boxing Association by Mr. Widner for 900 one color tickets and 900 one color tickets for the Golden Gloves Non-Profit Association at the Hippodrome Arena on February 7. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
